These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, strawberry
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person eating apricot is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | apricot   | strawberry   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate   |
| Sport      | weightlifting | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: corn, cucumber
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, house
1. the person eating corn is not to the left of the fan of house##8
2. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | cucumber | corn |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | house     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
